name: Setaris Corporation
overview:
Setaris builds technology businesses and the tools they run on. A successful product combines engineering, design and marketing. Setaris brings these elements together in a single package for their clients.

Strategy: A successful piece of technology combines effective design and precise engineering with solid business strategy. The Setaris concept architects pride themselves on their understanding of the technology market and will continue to assist clients even after their product is ready for market.

Design: The way a website or iPhone app looks and feels plays a tremendous role in its success. Setaris user experience and graphic designers help clients to create interfaces that are simple, beautiful and functionally elegant.

Engineering: Need to integrate a website with Facebook? Want a WordPress site to link up with a Mailchimp newsletter? Is geo-location the way to bring an iPhone app to the next level? The software engineers at Setaris will make it happen.
